SUMMARY:[Maine Secretary of State] Maine Secretary of State issues decisio
 n in challenge to Albert Joy nomination petitions for Knox County Sheriff
DESCRIPTION:Maine Secretary of State issues decision in challenge to Alber
 t Joy nomination petitions for Knox County Sheriff\n<span><span lang="lang
 ">jana.spaulding…</span></span>\n\n<span><time datetime="2026-06-18T17:0
 2:46-04:00" title="Thursday\, June 18\, 2026 - 17:02">Thu\, 06/18/2026 - 1
 7:02</time>\n</span>\n\n          <p><time datetime="2026-06-18T12:00:00Z"
 >6/18/2026</time>\n</p>\n    \n  <div>\n                  <div>\n         
  <p><strong>AUGUSTA\, Maine</strong> — Secretary of State Shenna Bellows
 <a href="https://www.maine.gov/sos/sites/maine.gov.sos/files/inline-files/
 6-18-2026%20-%20Final%20Decision%20Knox%20County%20Sheriff.pdf" title="6-1
 8-2026 - Final Decision Knox County Sheriff.pdf"> issued a decision</a> re
 garding a challenge to the nomination petitions filed by Albert Joy as a n
 on-party candidate for Knox County Sheriff. Secretary Bellows has rejected
  the challenge\, finding Mr. Joy eligible for the November ballot.</p><p>T
 he Secretary of State’s Office received the written challenge from Danie
 l Landers alleging that Mr. Joy did not meet the statutory qualifications 
 for the office of sheriff pursuant to Maine law. A hearing was held on Thu
 rsday\, June 11 with Chief Deputy Secretary Katherine McBrien serving as t
 he Presiding Officer at the hearing\, and Assistant Attorney General Jon B
 olton assisting as legal counsel. A recording on the hearing can be viewed
  on the Secretary of State’s YouTube page: <a href="https://gcc02.safel
 inks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40meseco
 fstate&data=05%7C02%7CJana.Spaulding%40maine.gov%7C7a896476b90940de2cee08d
 ecd726d98%7C413fa8ab207d4b629bcdea1a8f2f864e%7C0%7C0%7C639174088505267653%
 7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOi
 JXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&sdata=W0Erg%2B4pQ%
 2Blek9alZ4qobVj8IecZDSwJZeW5oSS0fZI%3D&reserved=0">https://www.youtube.com
 /@mesecofstate</a>. </p><p>The Secretary\, upon review of the proceedings
  and evidence\, the recommendation of the he\nhttps://www.maine.gov/sos/ne
 ws/maine-secretary-state-issues-decision-challenge-albert-joy-nomination-p
 etitions-knox-county
URL:https://www.maine.gov/sos/news/maine-secretary-state-issues-decision-c
 hallenge-albert-joy-nomination-petitions-knox-county
CATEGORIES:Maine Secretary of State
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
